1. This test will find a word that appears once in a one word string and output the number of times the specified word appears within the string.(input: fish and fish, output: 1);

2. This test will find a word that appears once in a multiple word string and output the number of times the specified word appears within the string. (input: fish and What a big fish., output: 1);

3. This test will find a word that appears more than once in a multiple word string and output the number of times the specified word appears within the string. (input: fish and One fish two fish, red fish blue fish., output: 4);
